---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Arthur Pfalzgraf - Ironing things out at MoonPay."
  description="Head of Product at Iron, acquired by MoonPay. High agency, fast iteration. Crypto, AI, and behavioral design nerd."
>
  <header class="page-header">
    <h1>Arthur Pfalzgraf</h1>
  </header>

  <section class="intro">
    <p>Ironing things out at MoonPay. Head of Product at Iron, acquired by MoonPay. High agency, fast iteration. I zoom out, then execute fast. Crypto, AI, and behavioral design nerd. Low tolerance for PowerPoint.</p>
  </section>

  <hr />

  <section class="work-history" aria-label="Work history">
    <article class="role">
      <h2><a href="https://iron.xyz" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Iron by MoonPay</a></h2>
      <div class="role-meta">HEAD OF PRODUCT · PRESENT</div>
      <p>Zero to one. Leading Product at Iron. Acquired by MoonPay in 6 months. Now building the stablecoin payments and institutional layer within MoonPay, rapidly aiming to become the market leader. Heads down building!</p>
    </article>

    <article class="role">
      <h2><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/posts/ultimateapp_big-news-jupiter-acquires-ultimate-wallet-activity-7188541907856240641-5liu?utm_source=share&utm_medium=member_desktop&rcm=ACoAAA_68j4B11gaLII1H8TTT7EGEWD8iHKRHH8" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Ultimate</a></h2>
      <div class="role-meta">PRODUCT · ACQUIRED BY JUPITER EXCHANGE</div>
      <p>Built the crypto trading wallet that set the standard for trading on-chain. Speed, dApp browser with smart search, MS-accurate candles. Acquired by Jupiter Exchange, the world's biggest decentralised exchange. Became a crypto degen.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="role">
      <h2><a href="https://traderepublic.com/en-de" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Trade Republic</a></h2>
      <div class="role-meta">PRODUCT MANAGER CRYPTO EXPANSION</div>
      <p>Led crypto expansion across Europe at one of its largest neobrokers. Built custody from scratch. Secured VASP licenses in 6 tier-1 markets — FR, DE, AT, NL, ES, IT — in under a year. Became an international crypto regulatory and compliance nerd.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="role">
      <h2><a href="https://www.hellofreshgroup.com/en/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">HelloFresh</a></h2>
      <div class="role-meta">PRODUCT DATA SCIENTIST → PRODUCT MANAGER</div>
      <p>First product analyst on HelloFresh's famous referral program (RAF). Grew into PM, launching 3+ new ventures from scratch, all EBITDA positive within 3 years. Became a data and behavioral design nerd.</p>
    </article>
  </section>

  <hr />

  <footer class="page-footer">
    <p>
      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/apfalzgraf/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn ↗</a>
      · <a href="https://github.com/Arthurpfz" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub ↗</a>
      · <a href="https://x.com/arthurpfz" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">X ↗</a>
    </p>
  </footer>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    padding: var(--space-lg) 0 var(--space-sm);
  }

  .tagline {
    font-size: var(--text-h2);
    margin-top: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .intro {
    padding-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .intro p {
    max-width: 680px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .work-history {
    margin: var(--space-sm) 0;
  }

  .role {
    padding: var(--space-lg) 0;
    border-bottom: var(--border);
  }

  .role:last-of-type {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .role-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .role-note {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-style: normal;
    font-size: var(--text-meta);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-meta);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .role-meta {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-style: normal;
    font-size: var(--text-meta);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-meta);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    opacity: 0.6;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .role p {
    max-width: 680px;
  }

  hr {
    margin: var(--space-md) 0;
  }

  .page-footer {
    padding: var(--space-lg) 0;
  }

  .page-footer p {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-style: normal;
    font-size: var(--text-meta);
    opacity: 0.45;
  }
</style>
